Package: bacenR
Title: Tools to Access Data from Banco Central do Brasil
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Theodoro", , "rtheodoro@usp.br", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6741-5153"))
Description: Provides functions to query, retrieve, and tidy economic and
    financial data from Banco Central do Brasil web services for use in R
    analyses and workflows.
